### Step 5.2 — Create SuitGlowController
🤖 Claude creates `StarterPlayer/StarterPlayerScripts/SuitGlowController` (LocalScript):

Listens for `UpdateSuitGlow` RemoteEvent from server:
- HP 100–60%: character Parts glow `Color3.new(0.27, 0.53, 1)` (blue)
- HP 59–30%: glow shifts to `Color3.new(1, 0.8, 0)` (yellow)
- HP 29–0%: glow pulses `Color3.new(1, 0.1, 0.1)` (red, heartbeat pulse)

Also plays heartbeat sound when HP < 30%, pitch increases as HP drops.

